    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver or a great project for someone looking to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and fading clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all essential electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it could benefit from a tune-up and some suspension work in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that is priced according to its current state.",
