    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or reliable secondary car for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine starts and runs, though it could benefit from a tune-up, and the transmission remains functional despite some occasional hesitation. Externally, there are visible scratches, a few minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows noticeable wear and one of the rear windows is currently non-operational. It is a dependable driver that reflects its age and mileage accurately.",
