    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This is, without exaggeration, a showroom-quality time capsule. Every inch of the original factory paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected since day one in a climate-controlled garage. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinct new-car scent; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any UV damage or fading. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history detailing every preventative maintenance milestone. The engine bay is pristine, and the transmission shifts with the crisp precision of a car that just rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it was first delivered.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
